      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This colonial-style helmet protects the wearer from jungle nuisances. The wearer is affected by a constant endure elements effect (as the spell, hot weather only) and gains a +4 competence bonus on saving throws against the distraction ability of swarms. In addition, once per day the wearer can conjure an invisible porter that acts as either a floating disk or an unseen servant (wearer's choice).<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, endure elements, floating disk, hide from animals, unseen servant</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Magical Marketplace",
